description: Wonderfully private 2 bedroom corner unit in the architecturally significant Residences at St. Augustine will captivate admirers of new and old alike. A perfect blend of character and modern amenities the open concept kitchen, dining, and living spaces boast premium appliances, finishes, and hardwood floors while high ceilings and towering windows provide abundant natural sunlight throughout. The gracious primary suite includes a full bathroom with double sink vanity and glass shower, plus a custom designed walk-in closet. Another full bathroom, in-unit laundry, and a 2nd bedroom, ready for duty as home office or nursery, round out the palatial quarters. With 2 deeded outdoor parking spots, a well equipped club room for work and entertainment, professional building management, and common areas with stunning views of the city skyline, residents enjoy proximity to all that Southie offers with convenience to highways and public transit. A must see trifecta of space, charm, and luxury.
